{% # Title block v1.2.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v1.2.0 — top-margin override range changed to `-100…100` (was `0…200`): negative values pull a block tighter than the section rhythm; the 100–200 push range is dropped (use a `spacer` block for larger gaps). Step stays 2 — Shopify caps ranges at 101 steps. Pairs with `utility--block-layout-vars` v1.2.0 (emit on `!= 0`). See `.context/docs/schema-conventions.md` § Top-spacing pair.
  - v1.1.0 — add `text_align` setting (start/center/end)
  - v1.0.0 — initial
{% endcomment %}

{% render 'title', section: section, block: block %}

